;Record of the Year
*"[[Video (song)|Video]]" - [[India.Arie]]
*"[[Fallin']]" - [[Alicia Keys]]
*'''"[[Walk On (U2 song)|Walk On]]" - [[U2]]'''
*"[[Ms. Jackson]]" - [[OutKast]]
*"[[Drops of Jupiter (Tell Me)|Drops of Jupiter]]" - [[Train (band)|Train]]

;Album of the Year
*''[[Acoustic Soul]]'' - [[India.Arie]]
*''[["Love and Theft"|Love and Theft]]'' - [[Bob Dylan]]
*''[[Stankonia]]'' - [[OutKast]]
*'''''[[O Brother, Where Art Thou? (soundtrack)|O Brother, Where Art Thou?]]'' - Various Artists'''
*''[[All That You Can't Leave Behind]]'' - [[U2]]

;Song of the Year
*"[[Video (song)|Video]]" - [[India.Arie]]
*"[[Drops of Jupiter (Tell Me)|Drops of Jupiter]]" - [[Train (band)|Train]]
*"[[Stuck in a Moment You Can't Get Out Of]]" - [[U2]]
