===Blues===
*[[Grammy Award for Best Traditional Blues Album|Best Traditional Blues Album]]
**John P. Hampton, Jared Tuten (engineers) & [[Jimmie Vaughan]] (producer & artist) for ''Do You Get the Blues?''
*[[Grammy Award for Best Contemporary Blues Album|Best Contemporary Blues Album]]
**[[Delbert McClinton]], [[Gary Nicholson (singer)|Gary Nicholson]] (producers), [[Richard Dodd]], Don Smith (engineers) & [[Delbert McClinton]] for ''Nothing Personal''

===Children's===
*[[Grammy Award for Best Musical Album for Children|Best Musical Album for Children]]
